{"calories":"540","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"Baked potatoes are one of our absolute favorite things to make and eat: super simple, reliably delicious, and entirely edible—skin and all! In this masterful mashup, we’re combining our love of the humble potato with another obsession: Marsala sauce. The spuds are baked with Gruyère cheese, then topped with the velvety mushroom-studded sauce, and served with a punchy arugula salad for added brightness. Meet your new favorite baked potato. ","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"04f2ba720e","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18395/Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18395/hero_Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18395/menu_small_Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18395/small_square_Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18395/medium_square_Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18395/recipe_profile_page_Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18398/Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18401/Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/18401/menu_small_Cheesy_Baked_Potatoes_with_Mushroom_Marsala_Sauce_and_Arugula_Salad_THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Cheesy Baked Potatoes with Mushroom Marsala Sauce and Arugula Salad","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"30-40","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"marsala-baked-potatoes-with-arugula-salad","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/10707/recipe_card20170127-4-kdezih.pdf","recipe_id":2086,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Cheesy Baked Potatoes","subtitle":"with Mushroom Marsala Sauce and Arugula Salad","title":"Cheesy Baked Potatoes","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eNo microwave? No problem! Wrap potatoes in foil and bake at 425°F until soft when pierced with a knife, about 1 hour. If baking, wait 30 minutes before continuing with rest of recipe, so the sauce doesn't over-reduce while your potatoes bake.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["12\" large pan","aluminum foil","baking sheet"],"id":2086,"ingredients":["russet potato","cremini mushrooms","parsley","lemon","unsalted butter","apple cider vinegar","honey","vegetable stock","Marsala wine","heavy cream","shredded Gruyère cheese","baby arugula"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"russet potato","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/484/medium_square_russet-potato.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"10.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"parsley","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1279/medium_square_medium_square_parsley-test.jpg"},{"name":"lemon","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/16/medium_square_LEMON_SLICED_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"apple cider vinegar","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/231/medium_square_APPLE_CIDER_VINEGAR_copy.jpg"},{"name":"honey","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/142/medium_square_HONEY_copy.jpg"},{"name":"vegetable stock","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/906/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_beef-broth.jpg"},{"name":"Marsala wine","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1309/medium_square_MARSALA_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"heavy cream","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/71/medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"},{"name":"shredded Gruyère cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/280/medium_square_dairy-gruyere1.jpg"},{"name":"baby arugula","quantity":"5.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1394/medium_square_medium_square_arugula-test.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":[],"pantry_items_full":[],"steps":[{"title":"Cook Potatoes","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17097/recipe_card_size_1._Bake_Potatoes.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 425ºF. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003epotatoes\u003c/strong\u003e, pierce all over with a fork, then place on a heat-safe plate (see Recipe Tip). Microwave until beginning to soften, about 5 minutes. Flip and continue to microwave until completely tender, about 5 minutes more.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17096/recipe_card_size_2._Prepare_Ingredients_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile potatoes soften, wipe \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e clean with a damp paper towel and cut into ¼-inch slices. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003eparsley\u003c/strong\u003e and roughly chop leaves, discarding stems. Halve \u003cstrong\u003elemon\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté Mushrooms and Make Salad Dressing","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17100/recipe_card_size_3._Cook_Mushrooms.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e in a large pan over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms \u003c/strong\u003eand sauté, stirring, until tender, about 8 minutes. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e¼ teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Meanwhile, in a large bowl, whisk \u003cstrong\u003eapple\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ecider\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003evinegar\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of honey \u003c/strong\u003eto combine. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e¼ teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e. Whisking continuously, slowly add \u003cstrong\u003e2 tablespoons olive oil \u003c/strong\u003euntil combined. Set aside.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make Marsala Sauce ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17099/recipe_card_size_4._Make_Marsala_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003evegetable stock \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003eMarsala \u003c/strong\u003eto pan with mushrooms and bring to a boil over medium-high heat. Cook, stirring occasionally, until liquid is reduced by ⅔, 5-6 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ecream\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eparsley\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ejuice of 1 lemon\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring, until sauce thickens, about 1 minute more. Reduce heat to very low, stirring occasionally, until ready to serve. \u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Melt Cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17098/recipe_card_size_5._Melt_Cheese_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile sauce reduces, place softened \u003cstrong\u003epotatoes\u003c/strong\u003e on a foil-lined baking sheet. Cut a cross into tops of potatoes, going down about halfway through. Gently squeeze in sides of potatoes to puff up the middle. Arrange \u003cstrong\u003epotatoes\u003c/strong\u003e close together on baking sheet and sprinkle over \u003cstrong\u003eGruyère\u003c/strong\u003e. Bake until potatoes are warmed through and cheese is golden brown, about 6 minutes.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Toss Salad and Plate","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17101/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Potatoes.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile cheese melts, add \u003cstrong\u003earugula \u003c/strong\u003eto bowl with dressing and toss to coat. Spoon \u003cstrong\u003emushroom Marsala sauce \u003c/strong\u003eover \u003cstrong\u003echeesy baked potatoes \u003c/strong\u003eand serve with \u003cstrong\u003earugula salad\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in! Discard remaining honey.\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""},{"name":"\u003c 600 Calories","slug":"low-calorie","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Vegetable","slug":"vegetable","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""},{"name":"\u003c 600 Calories","slug":"low-calorie","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}